{"tid":1364180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《震驚原居民》沉重哀悼 李鵬同志","createTime":"2019-07-25T09:58:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T11:43:15.000Z","uid":263218,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9e662c183f144303864433588a268e083e4f668b","tid":1364180,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:58:57.000Z","msg":"悼文： <br />\n<br />\n李鵬同志 升天離逝的消息，震驚了我中華十四億人。李鵬同志作為共產主義的先鋒，愛國愛黨的好榜樣，在90歲壯年之際離逝，深感悲痛。<br />\n<br />\n李鵬同志，一生之功莫過於埋沒個人道德良知，換取我黨成就大業。即使李鵬同志冒著下地獄的可能，仍敢於開槍，敢於鎮壓，這種政治想法非正常人所有。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，一眾連登的愛國愛黨網民，懷著悲痛的心，將於2019年7月27日去深深懷念。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f8707c19e3bc357cb3c7d67806ab23e3cc6c32","tid":1364180,"uid":263218,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:01:45.000Z","msg":"天妒英才 咁早死左<br />\n應該訓多兩年病床 見證一帶一路的成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1715b8dd907963c335455e591fe0b0b7ab20153d","tid":1364180,"uid":176092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:02:53.000Z","msg":"歡迎去元朗西鐵站下面連儂牆寫上祝福字句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f882713a869782606581f638c65b3ccd9e254a","tid":1364180,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1715b8dd907963c335455e591fe0b0b7ab20153d","tid":1364180,"uid":176092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:02:53.000Z","msg":"歡迎去元朗西鐵站下面連儂牆寫上祝福字句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:03:30.000Z","msg":"屌你個西 還我李鵬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a5902c32a7f8eea7a6cd2daf999876165e363d","tid":1364180,"uid":274658,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:04:02.000Z","msg":"英年早逝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本來應該有百二歲命"},{"pid":"ffb3a2ad777413f5613205c67941c36b5e8cd952","tid":